Figure 1: A ring chart reflecting the best average kills, assistances, deaths, farms among all main bottom-lane players.



As we can see from Figure 1.
The bottom-lane player Viper from team EDG and Gala from the team RNG has the highest average kills, which means he could kill 4 enemy champions per game.
The bottom-lane player Betty from team RW and Lwx from the team FPX has the highest average assistance, which means he could help his teammates to kill 6.9 enemy champions per game.
The bottom-lane player huanfeng from team SN has the lowest average deaths, which means he could only die 1.2 per game.
The bottom-lane player Lwx from team FPX and Kepler from the team V5 has the highest farming, which means he could kill 440 enemy units per game.
2. Discover
