Figure 2: A radar diagram comparing the data of bottom-lane players of the top five teams.



As we can see from Table 1 and Figure 2:
These five bottom-lane players have their own specialty in terms of ability, Viper from team EDG focus more on vision, Lwx from team FPX focus more on farming, Gala from team RNG is a balanced bottom-lane player, Light from team LNG has highest KDA, Elk from team WE has most MVP.
A fun fact we can see from Figure 2 is that Viper,Light have the same amount of KDA (though KDA of Gala and Elk is same too, we prefer higher KDA), now we put more attention on their exact kills, deaths and assistances, to see if there exists some difference between them.
Note: The formula to calculate the amount of KDA is: \[ egin{equation}
\ KDA =  rac{Kill(total) + Assistance(total)}{Death(total)}
\end{equation}\]



